---
---

<section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="main-headline reveal-up">
            <span class="we-make-it">We make it</span>
            <span class="typed-text-container">
                <span class="typed-text"></span>
                <span class="cursor">&nbsp;</span>
            </span>
        </h1>
        <h2 class="sub-headline reveal-up delay-1">AI 기반 교육 솔루션 · 워크플로우 자동화</h2>
        <p class="description reveal-up delay-2">
            복잡한 인공지능 기술을 현장에서 바로 사용할 수 있는 실체로 구현합니다.<br>
            문제 제작부터 학원 관리까지, 교육의 모든 과정을 '작동'하게 만드는 기술 파트너, 프론티어웍스.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-group reveal-up delay-3">
            <a href="#solutions" class="btn-primary btn-large">솔루션 보기</a>
            <a href="#about" class="btn-secondary btn-large">회사 소개</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-indicator reveal-up delay-4">
        <div class="mouse"></div>
        <p>Scroll to explore</p>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    const text = "work.";
    const typedTextElement = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.typed-text');
    let charIndex = 0;

    function typeEffect() {
        if (!typedTextElement) return;
        typedTextElement.textContent = text.substring(0, charIndex + 1);
        charIndex++;

        if (charIndex === text.length) {
            const cursor = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.cursor');
            if (cursor) cursor.style.animation = "blink 1s step-end infinite";
            return;
        }

        setTimeout(typeEffect, 150);
    }

    setTimeout(typeEffect, 1000);
</script>

<style>
    .hero {
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        z-index: 10;
    }

    .main-headline {
        font-size: 5rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .we-make-it {
        font-weight: 300;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .typed-text-container {
        font-weight: 900;
        display: inline-block;
        min-width: 200px;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .typed-text {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-accent-1), var(--color-accent-2));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .cursor {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 4px;
        background-color: var(--color-accent-2);
        margin-left: 4px;
        animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0; }
    }

    .sub-headline {
        font-family: var(--font-ko);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .description {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .cta-group {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .scroll-indicator {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        opacity: 0.5;
        animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    }

    .scroll-indicator p {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        font-family: var(--font-en);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .mouse {
        width: 26px;
        height: 40px;
        border: 2px solid #fff;
        border-radius: 15px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .mouse::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        width: 4px;
        height: 4px;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        top: 8px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        animation: scroll 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scroll {
        0% { transform: translate(-50%, 0); opacity: 1; }
        100% { transform: translate(-50%, 15px); opacity: 0; }
    }

    @keyframes bounce {
        0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .main-headline {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
        }
        .sub-headline {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
